CLOSEDeveloping story (Photo: The Republic)Phoenix police are investigating after a vehicle crashed into a pole Tuesday evening, killing the driver, according to Phoenix Police Department Sgt.
Police say the driver was heading north on 31st Avenue and collided with a pole at the corner of Voltaire Avenue, near Thunderbird Road.
Phoenix Fire Department crews attempted to extricate an unidentified man but he died at the scene.
